com.facebook.buck.cxx.toolchain.nativelink

Class NativeLinkableInput

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.cxx.toolchain.nativelink.NativeLinkableInput

  • @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
 @Generated(value={"Immutables.generator","AbstractNativeLinkableInput"})
 @Immutable
 @CheckReturnValue
public final class NativeLinkableInput
extends Object
    A class containing inputs to be passed to the native linker. Dependencies (e.g. C++ libraries) of a top-level native linkable rule (e.g. C++ binary) can use this to contribute components to the final link.
